'''César Augusto Yanis Velasco''' (born 28 January 1996) is a Panamanian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as [[Midfielder#Winger|left winger]] for Chilean club [[C.D. Cobresal|Cobresal]], on loan from Costa Rican club [[A.D. San Carlos|San Carlos]], and the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]].

==Club career==
Born in [[Panama City]], Yanis played for local sides [[San Francisco F.C.|San Francisco]], [[Unión Deportivo Universitario|Chorrillo]] and [[Costa del Este F.C.|Costa del Este]]. On 31 August 2021, he moved abroad and joined Spanish [[Segunda División]] side [[Real Zaragoza]] on a one-year loan deal.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.realzaragoza.com/noticias/acuerdo-para-la-incorporaci-n-del-extremo-paname-o-c-sar-yanis|title=Acuerdo para la incorporación del extremo panameño César Yanis|trans-title=Agreement for the signing of Panamanian winger César Yanis|publisher=Real Zaragoza|language=es|date=31 August 2021|accessdate=31 August 2021}}</ref>

In 2025, Yanis moved to Chile and joined [[C.D. Cobresal|Cobresal]] on loan from [[A.D. San Carlos|San Carlos]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Vega |first1=Diego |title=Cobresal ficha a un seleccionado: jugó en Europa y tiene 28 años |url=https://chile.as.com/futbol/cobresal-ficha-a-un-seleccionado-jugo-en-europa-y-tiene-28-anos-n/ |access-date=27 December 2024 |work=[[Diario AS]] |date=26 December 2024 |language=es}}</ref> In December 2025, he renewed with them for a season.<ref>{{cite news |title=César Yanis renueva con el Cobresal por una temporada más |url=https://www.rpctv.com/futbol-internacional/futbol/cesar-yanis-renueva-el-cobresal-una-temporada-mas-n6063475 |access-date=25 December 2025 |work=www.rpctv.com |date=11 December 2025 |language=es}}</ref>

==International career==
Yanis made his debut for the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]] in a 0–0 friendly tie with [[Nicaragua national football team|Nicaragua]] on 26 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/26/world/non-fifa-friendlies/nicaragua/panama/3211005/|title=Nicaragua vs. Panama – 26 February 2020 – Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref>

On 17 July 2021, Yanis scored his first goal for Panama against [[Honduras national football team|Honduras]].<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.espn.com.mx/futbol/partido/_/juegoId/602706
|title=Honduras vs. Panama – 17 July 2021 – ESPN |website= espn.com}}</ref>

